  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 84736f00ca5690940aa2333ea4ce800b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dream2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - "Then it always goes to that night. \nWhen I found her alone in the treehouse,
    our treehouse."
  - "I think she blamed herself for my arm, for what happened to Mom... \nIt wasn't
    anyones' fault, but I don't think she could accept that."
  - That's when she double downed into her hero pursuits. When she started skipping
    grades. This gap between us formed...
